Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Ilaya-Ivisan Elementary School in the Municipality of Ivisan, Province of Capiz, to Don Juan S. Jarencio Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 655
An Act Changing the Name of the Ilaya-Ivisan Elementary School in the Municipality of Ivisan, Province of Capiz, to Don Juan S. Jarencio Memorial School
Section 1. The Ilaya-Ivisan Elementary School in the Municipality of Ivisan, Province of Capiz, shall be known as the Don Juan S. Jarencio Memorial School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
